      "comment": "RINSED THE LOT (6) is a talented dog who is a winner of 13 races but missed the frame last time when sixth at Q Lakeside (26.40). Hard to knock his form from this box, unbeaten in two starts. Rates on top in this line up. ARMARTA (4) has a strong record this track and trip with 13 wins and two placings from 17 starts. Missed the frame latest (26.02) when fifth over 457m at Q Lakeside in a Grade 5. Can hit the frame with the right run. HIGH FIVE LAD (8) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (19.86) at this track behind Move It Georgia in a Grade 3/4. Bold showing expected. CASINO SPECIAL (1) is a course and distance winner with definite claims.",
